1. Problem Understanding & Scope
1.1 Platform Overview
XYZ is building a dual-sided online movie ticket booking marketplace:
•	B2B Side: Theatre partners onboard their venues, manage shows, seat inventory, and pricing
•	B2C Side: End customers browse movies across cities/languages/genres and book tickets

